---
import { profileConfig, siteConfig } from '../config'
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const pageTitle = `About | ${siteConfig.title}`
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 space-y-24">
    <!-- Hero Section with Grid Background -->
    <section class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center py-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-background -z-10"></div>
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src={profileConfig.avatar} 
            alt={profileConfig.name} 
            class="rounded-2xl w-64 h-64 object-cover animated-border glow mx-auto"
          />
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-2/3 space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">
          Hi, I'm {profileConfig.name}
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 leading-relaxed">
          {profileConfig.bio}
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
          {profileConfig.links.map(link => (
            <a 
              href={link.url} 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class={`text-3xl transition-transform hover:scale-110 ${link.color} glow`}
              aria-label={link.name}
            >
              {link.name === 'GitHub' && (
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M12 2A10 10 0 0 0 2 12c0 4.42 2.87 8.17 6.84 9.5c.5.08.66-.23.66-.5v-1.69c-2.77.6-3.36-1.34-3.36-1.34c-.46-1.16-1.11-1.47-1.11-1.47c-.91-.62.07-.6.07-.6c1 .07 1.53 1.03 1.53 1.03c.87 1.52 2.34 1.07 2.91.83c.09-.65.35-1.09.63-1.34c-2.22-.25-4.55-1.11-4.55-4.92c0-1.11.38-2 1.03-2.71c-.1-.25-.45-1.29.1-2.64c0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.02c.79-.22 1.65-.33 2.5-.33c.85 0 1.71.11 2.5.33c1.91-1.29 2.75-1.02 2.75-1.02c.55 1.35.2 2.39.1 2.64c.65.71 1.03 1.6 1.03 2.71c0 3.82-2.34 4.66-4.57 4.91c.36.31.69.92.69 1.85V21c0 .27.16.59.67.5C19.14 20.16 22 16.42 22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2Z"/></svg>
              )}
              {link.name === 'LinkedIn' && (
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14m-.5 15.5v-5.3a3.26 3.26 0 0 0-3.26-3.26c-.85 0-1.84.52-2.32 1.3v-1.11h-2.79v8.37h2.79v-4.93c0-.77.62-1.4 1.39-1.4a1.4 1.4 0 0 1 1.4 1.4v4.93h2.79M6.88 8.56a1.68 1.68 0 0 0 1.68-1.68c0-.93-.75-1.69-1.68-1.69a1.69 1.69 0 0 0-1.69 1.69c0 .93.76 1.68 1.69 1.68m1.39 9.94v-8.37H5.5v8.37h2.77Z"/></svg>
              )}
              {link.name === 'Twitter' && (
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" d="M22.46 6c-.77.35-1.6.58-2.46.69c.88-.53 1.56-1.37 1.88-2.38c-.83.5-1.75.85-2.72 1.05C18.37 4.5 17.26 4 16 4c-2.35 0-4.27 1.92-4.27 4.29c0 .34.04.67.11.98C8.28 9.09 5.11 7.38 3 4.79c-.37.63-.58 1.37-.58 2.15c0 1.49.75 2.81 1.91 3.56c-.71 0-1.37-.2-1.95-.5v.03c0 2.08 1.48 3.82 3.44 4.21a4.22 4.22 0 0 1-1.93.07a4.28 4.28 0 0 0 4 2.98a8.521 8.521 0 0 1-5.33 1.84c-.34 0-.68-.02-1.02-.06C3.44 20.29 5.7 21 8.12 21C16 21 20.33 14.46 20.33 8.79c0-.19 0-.37-.01-.56c.84-.6 1.56-1.36 2.14-2.23Z"/></svg>
              )}
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Me Section -->
    <section class="modern-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 section-header bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">About Me</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">
        <p>
          My journey into the world of AI, ML, and data engineering began with a simple question: "How can we make data work smarter, not harder?" This curiosity led me to discover the transformative power of data-driven decision making during my early career at Accenture, where I witnessed firsthand how data could revolutionize business operations.
        </p>
        <p>
          What truly ignited my passion was a challenging project where I developed an automated extract, transform, load (ETL) pipeline for analyzing 1,000+ vendor datasets. The moment I saw how this solution reduced manual processing time from weeks to hours while uncovering previously hidden business insights, I knew I had found my calling. This experience taught me that the real magic happens when we combine technical expertise with business acumen to create solutions that drive tangible value.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, as a senior data engineer, I specialize in building scalable data infrastructures that power AI systems. My approach combines cutting-edge technologies with practical business solutions, focusing on three key areas:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Designing and implementing robust data pipelines that handle real-time processing at scale</li>
          <li>Developing artificial intelligence/machine learning (AI/ML) models that transform raw data into actionable insights</li>
          <li>Creating intuitive data visualizations that make complex information accessible to stakeholders</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          What sets me apart is my ability to bridge the gap between technical complexity and business value. I believe that the best data solutions are those that not only work efficiently but also drive meaningful business outcomes. Whether I'm optimizing a data warehouse, implementing a new Machine Learning model, or designing a data visualization dashboard, my goal is always to create solutions that empower organizations to make better, data-driven decisions.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not immersed in data, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, or sharing my knowledge through technical blog posts. I'm passionate about making data science and AI accessible to everyone, believing that the democratization of these technologies will lead to more innovative solutions and better business outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills Section -->
    <section class="modern-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 section-header bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {profileConfig.skills.map(skill => (
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">{skill.category}</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {skill.items.map(item => (
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
                  {item}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience Section -->
    <section class="modern-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 section-header bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Professional Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        {profileConfig.experience.map(job => (
          <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-blue-600 dark:border-blue-400">
            <div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full -left-[9px] top-1"></div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">{job.title}</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center">
                <p class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{job.company}</p>
                <p class="text-sm bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{job.period}</p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{job.description}</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 pl-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">
                {job.achievements?.map(achievement => (
                  <li>{achievement}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Education Section -->
    <section class="modern-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 section-header bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Education</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        {profileConfig.education.map(edu => (
          <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-blue-600 dark:border-blue-400">
            <div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full -left-[9px] top-1"></div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">{edu.degree}</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{edu.school}</p>
              <p class="text-sm bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full inline-block">{edu.period}</p>
              {edu.specialization && (
                <p class="text-md font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">Specialization: {edu.specialization}</p>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Certifications Section -->
    <section class="modern-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 section-header bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Certifications</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {profileConfig.certifications?.map(cert => (
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center gap-4 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full p-3 text-white">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path fill="currentColor" d="M248 128a56 56 0 0 1-56 56a8 8 0 0 1-8-8a8 8 0 0 1 8-8a40 40 0 0 0 0-80a8 8 0 0 1-8-8a8 8 0 0 1 8-8a56 56 0 0 1 56 56ZM56 72a8 8 0 0 0-8 8a8 8 0 0 0 8 8a40 40 0 0 1 0 80a8 8 0 0 0-8 8a8 8 0 0 0 8 8a56 56 0 0 0 0-112Zm72 112a56.06 56.06 0 0 1-56-56a8 8 0 0 1 16 0a40 40 0 0 0 80 0a8 8 0 0 1 16 0a56.06 56.06 0 0 1-56 56Zm0-112a56.06 56.06 0 0 1 56 56a8 8 0 0 1-16 0a40 40 0 0 0-80 0a8 8 0 0 1-16 0a56.06 56.06 0 0 1 56-56Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">{cert.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">{cert.issuer} â€¢ {cert.date}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <section class="modern-card p-10 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-background opacity-5"></div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">
        I'm always open to discussing new projects, opportunities, and collaborations. If you're interested in working together, feel free to reach out!
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contact" 
        class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-purple-700 hover:from-blue-800 hover:to-purple-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-md"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>